Subject: BoF: The Expanse is Saved
Description: Birds of a Feather: The Expanse was on SyFy then cancelled. Soon it was picked up by Amazon Prime after a media promotion by fans. Will we be able to expand SciFi using the media promotion of other great shows? What have we learned about getting funding and attention for our favorites? Can we do more?  Speakers include:Gibson Nichols - Track: Media  - Duration: 1 hour

Subject: Solar Panel Panel: Begin the Revolution and Make Money
Description: Solar is becoming the cheap way to create energy, but is it profitable?  Speakers include:Gibson Nichols - Track: Tech  - Duration: 1 hour
